donations.donation_comment: Appuyons les camionneurs et les organisations pacifiques qui les supportent. Écoutons les experts médicaux et les dirigeants qui le disent de plus en plus : les mesures comme le passeport sanitaire et la vaccination coercitive sont non seulement discriminatoires, mais aussi inefficaces. Le Canada doit apprendre à vivre avec le virus comme plusieurs autres pays sur la planète le font actuellement.
We are praying for you, truckers and your stand for freedom!!  God bless you!

Thank you for standing up for all of us who believe in human rights and freedoms.  Under God, we are indivisible.  We support you and stand with you.  May God protect you from the clutches of all enemies visible and invisible.
Thank you for being the face of freedom around the world.  We stand with you!  Brilliant idea!!!  You are our heroes and are single handedly saving freedom!  Rock on brothers and sisters!
Thanks for standing up for our rights!

Thank you to all the Truckers and everyone every where who is standing up for our freedoms and what we lost that should have never been taken away. "Being brave isn't supposed to be easy, but it's the key to moving forward."
